	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >Ok, I'm not a monk, never played one, nor a warrior.<br />
<br />
So can someone explain to me in the simplest terms what exactly is Damage Mitigation ( Combat Stability ) and Damage Avoidance ( Combat Agility ) and how they work.<br />
<br />
PS. and Yes i used search but only came up with the AA list on skills not what they are.</font></p>
	
